query:
SELECT t.id as turmaId, f.id as formandoId, f.nome, e.id as eventoId 
FROM turmas t 
JOIN formandos f ON f.turmaId = t.id 
LEFT JOIN eventos e ON e.turmaId = t.id 
WHERE t.codigo = '654' AND f.nome LIKE '%Jean-Karlo%' 
LIMIT 1
